(25, 'Chuột Bluetooth Logitech M337', 23, 12, 'chuot-bluetooth-logitech-m337', 'chuot-bluetooth-logitech-m337.jpg', '<h3>Giới thiệu sản phẩm</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/chuot-may-tinh\" target=\"_blank\">Chu&ocirc;̣t</a>&nbsp;bluetooth Logitech M337 đến từ h&atilde;ng uy t&iacute;n</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/86/156958/chuo-t-bluetooth-logitech-m337-1.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Chuột bluetooth Logitech M337 đến từ hãng uy tín\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/86/156958/chuo-t-bluetooth-logitech-m337-1.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/86/156958/chuo-t-bluetooth-logitech-m337-6.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Chuột bluetooth Logitech M337 đến từ hãng uy tín\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/86/156958/chuo-t-bluetooth-logitech-m337-6.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>K&iacute;ch thước chuột</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/86/156958/chuo-t-bluetooth-logitech-m337-2.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Chuột bluetooth Logitech M337 đến từ hãng uy tín\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/86/156958/chuo-t-bluetooth-logitech-m337-2.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/86/156958/chuo-t-bluetooth-logitech-m337-5.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Chuột bluetooth Logitech M337 đến từ hãng uy tín\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/86/156958/chuo-t-bluetooth-logitech-m337-5.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/86/156958/chuo-t-bluetooth-logitech-m337-3.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Chuột bluetooth Logitech M337 đến từ hãng uy tín\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/86/156958/chuo-t-bluetooth-logitech-m337-3.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Chi tiết kết nối</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/86/156958/chuot-b